description: Support to private sector development is one of the major components of enhanced economic growth theme under the Ethiopia UNDAF.

subproject.corporate outcome: Policies, strategies and partnerships established to enhance public-private sector collaboration and private sector and market development that benefit the poor and ensure that low-income households and small enterprises have access to a broad range of financial and legal services
subproject.description: The project will strengthen capacity for private sector through support that include enhancing capacity for public-private dialogue, and institutional strengthening of the chambers and women entrepreneurs,  the leather industry, and studying establishment of  free trade area among countries of the Sana'a forum.
subproject.title: Private Sector Development
